Also, you&#39;re using some 25+ year old syntax, which you really should abandon. [Don&#39;t set up your events inline with HTML][2] and [don&#39;t use `.getElementsByClassName()`][3].

&lt;!-- begin snippet: js hide: false console: true babel: false --&gt;

&lt;!-- language: lang-html --&gt;

